 discover serendipitously a highly variable X-ray source\nwhich has decreased its flux within a year by more than a factor of eight. This\nsource is most probably an AGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 May 2022 16:08:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
