ustered to propose several best\ncandidates for continuous energy generation. This work represents the first\nstudy on PEH design optimisation for real operational conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 02:33:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 05:58:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
