esented in the form of\nPareto fronts in three design spaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 05:31:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 22:16:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-19"}
