\nseveral hundred basis functions verify our suggestions concerning CD in case of\nfinite and perturbative magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 10:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-17"}
