according to other alternative\ntheories. A larger sample of galaxies will be needed to fully determine the\nabsence of any external field effect in NFDG.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 05:23:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2022 07:32:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
