 healthy people, and further studies are needed to\nreveal the associated factor of high NLR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 May 2022 20:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 20:53:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-29"}
